        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />        <title>Acorn - AI That Works For You</title>
        <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
        <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
        <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=EB+Garamond:wght@400;500&family=Inter:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
    </head>
    <body>
        <nav>
            <div class="nav-logo">
  <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
    <path d="M12 2C9 5 7 8 7 12c0 3.5 2 6 5 7 3-1 5-3.5 5-7 0-4-2-7-5-10z" fill="currentColor"/>
    <path d="M12 9v13" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4" stroke-linecap="round"/>
  </svg>
  <span>ACORN</span>
</div>
            <a href="#waitlist" class="nav-btn">Join Waitlist</a>
        </nav>

        <section class="hero">
            <p class="hero-label">ROOTED INTELLIGENCE</p>
            <h1>Does your AI work for you?</h1>
            <p class="hero-sub">Acorn is a business-first AI operating system that lives in Slack, and is loyal to you, not big tech.</p>
            <div class="hero-buttons">
                <a href="#waitlist" class="btn-primary">Join the Acorn Waitlist</a>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section class="control-context">
            <div class="cc-grid">
                <div class="cc-card">
                    <h3>Control</h3>
                    <p>Your data is yours. Acorn runs in your cloud, on your terms. No co-mingling, no model training on your private conversations. True data sovereignty.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="cc-card">
                    <h3>Context</h3>
                    <p>Acorn reads what you allow it to read: Slack, Drive, Notion, email. It builds a private model of your business, learning your team, your projects, and your voice.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
		<section class="orientation">
            <div class="orient-grid">
                <div class="orient-text">
                    <p class="section-label">THE FRAMEWORK</p>
                    <h2>Orientation beats delegation.</h2>
                    <p>Most people use AI to delegate tasks. Faster email, faster docs, no real thinking. Acorn is different. It uses the OODA loop: Observe, Orient, Decide, Act. Your AI doesn't just do what you say. It understands why.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="orient-diagram">
                    <div class="loop-step">Observe</div>
                    <div class="loop-step">Orient</div>
                    <div class="loop-step">Decide</div>
                    <div class="loop-step">Act</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
		<section class="meet-acorn">
            <p class="section-label">MEET YOUR CHIEF OF STAFF</p>
            <h2>An AI that knows your business.</h2>
            <div class="chat-mock">
                <div class="chat-bubble user-bubble">What's our top priority this week?</div>
                <div class="chat-bubble acorn-bubble">Based on your Q2 targets and yesterday's client call with Martinez, closing the proposal revision is the highest-leverage move. Want me to draft the updated scope?</div>
            </div>
        </section>
		<section class="trust">
            <p class="section-label">TRUST MODEL</p>
            <h2>How trust is earned.</h2>
            <div class="trust-grid">
                <div class="trust-card">
                    <h3>Act and Report</h3>
                    <p>For routine tasks within its authority, Acorn acts first and tells you what it did. No bottleneck. No waiting.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="trust-card">
                    <h3>Propose and Wait</h3>
                    <p>For decisions that need your judgment, Acorn presents options and waits for your call. It never overreaches.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="trust-card">
                    <h3>Escalate</h3>
                    <p>When something falls outside its scope, Acorn flags it immediately. No guessing. No pretending to know.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
		<section class="why-acorn">
            <div class="why-inner">
                <p class="section-label">THE VISION</p>
                <h2>Why Acorn exists.</h2>
                <blockquote>"The 7-figure business owner is the most underserved person in AI. Enterprise gets custom builds. Consumers get ChatGPT. The founder running a real business with real employees and real risk? Nobody is building for them. Until now."</blockquote>
                <p class="attribution">Brian Keith, Founder</p>
            </div>
        </section>
		<section class="waitlist" id="waitlist">
            <p class="section-label">GET EARLY ACCESS</p>
            <h2>Join the Acorn Waitlist.</h2>
            <p class="waitlist-sub">Be among the first founders to deploy a sovereign AI system built for your business.</p>
            <form accept-charset="UTF-8" action="https://redbeard.infusionsoft.com/app/form/process/8bce157b4a83074b0edda9c55e1ed0ba" class="infusion-form waitlist-form" id="inf_form_8bce157b4a83074b0edda9c55e1ed0ba" method="POST">
                <input name="inf_form_xid" type="hidden" value="8bce157b4a83074b0edda9c55e1ed0ba" />
                <input name="inf_thank_you" type="hidden" value="https://buyacorn.com/welcome.html" />
                <input name="inf_form_name" type="hidden" value="BuyAcorn.com Waitlist" />
                <input name="infusionsoft_version" type="hidden" value="1.70.0.942760" />
                <input id="inf_field_Email" name="inf_field_Email" placeholder="Enter your email" type="email" required />
                <button class="btn-primary infusion-recaptcha" id="recaptcha_8bce157b4a83074b0edda9c55e1ed0ba" type="submit">Join the Waitlist</button>
                <input type="text" name="inf-sbt" style="display:none !important;" />
            </form>
        </section>

        <footer>
            <div class="footer-inner">
                <div class="footer-logo">
  <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
    <path d="M12 2C9 5 7 8 7 12c0 3.5 2 6 5 7 3-1 5-3.5 5-7 0-4-2-7-5-10z" fill="currentColor"/>
    <path d="M12 9v13" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4" stroke-linecap="round"/>
  </svg>
  <span>ACORN</span>
</div>
